The best of the 3rd gen "all stainless steel" 9mm autos from Smith and Wesson, the Tactical 5906 was built specifically for Law Enforcement and was made to their Performance Center standards with the slide and frame cut from the same block of stainless and staying together throughout the manufacturing process.
